gitCommit.subject: Refactor Docker setup for optimized performance and resource management. Updated docker-compose.yml to enhance service initialization, added common environment variables, and improved health checks. Transitioned from 'talib' to 'ta' library for technical analysis in backend services, ensuring better compatibility and performance. Modified Dockerfile for multi-stage builds, reducing image size and improving security with non-root user execution. Updated run_tests.sh to reflect new dependencies.
